 11 个频道计算的。<br> *由于YouTube上的数据存在错误以及对上周汇总错误的更正，可能会有一些数据显示出下降而不是上升。感谢您的理解。</figcaption></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td> <strong>回复：行动</strong><br>（三井）<br> ——<br>・人才渠道 ・官方渠道<br><br></td><td><strong>22</strong><br> ——<br> 23<br> ├22<br> └1<br> (±0)</td><td> <strong>58,063</strong> (+143)<br> （1,277,375 人中）<br> 1,308,375 ├1,277,375 └30,100 (+3,144)△</td></tr></tbody></table><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> *如果下周平均注册人数低于前 30 名，Re:Act 数据将停止提供。 </figcaption></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="euVHXkvNOH"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-english-3rd-gen-new-5-vtuber-advent-debut/">Holo Live英语第3代新人VTuber《Advent》5人登场</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Holo Live英语第三代新人VTuber“Advent”5首次亮相” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/hololive-english-3rd-gen-new-5-vtuber-advent-debut/embed/#?secret=YffEnePUsE#?secret=euVHXkvNOH" data-secret="euVHXkvNOH" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="gzcCpHBVQH"><a href="https://p2y.jp/neo-porte-terminated-contract-of-vtuber-nayuta/">解除与 Neo-Porte 所属 VTuber“武藤凪”的合约</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Neo-Porte 旗下 VTuber “Nagimuto”取消了合同” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/neo-porte-terminated-contract-of-vtuber-nayuta/embed/#?secret=iF5OBG5L8E#?secret=gzcCpHBVQH" data-secret="gzcCpHBVQH" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed i