・アビスガードさんのデビュー初配信は、7月31日12時45分。新たな道を切り拓けるか、FUWAMOCOの挑戦が始まります。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/fuwamoco_en/status/1684065588598145027" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc_90dWbP7qjkThF4wLgBLMKVACOToHf7WKkqTFDvxGUs36J6cZxfkI-G8nsMtIwdrVhBaGw5UIZennO8F-X-Z9mGxWh4yPZwNx7l_d-gxEEliUzX8UQNs6dOYS3vxVNhzo0VkkJh5V3iGo2kOQJ7luZ=w1097-h1197-s-no" alt=""/></a> </figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="A74beLW5CI"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-english-3rd-gen-vtuber-advent-debut-find-out-why-no-newcomers-have-come-before/">ホロライブEnglish 3期生VTuber「Advent」デビュー ここまで新人が見送られてきた背景を探る</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="&#8220;ホロライブEnglish 3期生VTuber「Advent」デビュー ここまで新人が見送られてきた背景を探る&#8221; &#8212; P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/hololive-english-3rd-gen-vtuber-advent-debut-find-out-why-no-newcomers-have-come-before/embed/#?secret=Wty8ps8inL#?secret=A74beLW5CI" data-secret="A74beLW5CI" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="nKQdoKW3pS"><a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-english-3rd-gen-new-5-vtuber-advent-debut/">ホロライブEnglish 3期生新人VTuber「Advent」5名がデビュー</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="&#8220;ホロライブEnglish 3期生新人VTuber「Advent」5名がデビュー&#8221; &#8212; P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/hololive-english-3rd-gen-new-5-vtuber-advent-debut/embed/#?secret=NUl5s7DKly#?secret=nKQdoKW3pS" data-secret="nKQdoKW3pS" width="600" height="338" frame